    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/828e4961a2562ff5cccfa516df36a602.poster.avif?t=1749610118\" width=616 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/828e4961a2562ff5cccfa516df36a602.webm?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Once Upon A Time...</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This was once a beautiful digital world. But that was before the A.I. showed up and destroyed everything. With calculated, emotionless precision, the A.I. began to systematically consume everything in the world. It started replacing the unique digital life with it's own pale regurgitated slop. Before long the once vibrant world was unrecognizable. It has become a wasteland filled with soulless machines designed to endlessly consume. A land where almost all hope had been lost.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But from the darkness, a hero emerges. You are Dark Pixel, the last of the digital life that was native to these lands. You are the last remaining opposition. Will you be able to find a way to stop the machine? Or is the A.I.'s victory inevitable? Only you can decide. The power is in your hands. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/cea199123f1798b269bd290382e3ff68.poster.avif?t=1749610118\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/cea199123f1798b269bd290382e3ff68.webm?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/cea199123f1798b269bd290382e3ff68.mp4?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Modern Platforming Classic</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Pixel is a love letter to retro platforming games, with a stylized minimalist aesthetic filled with tight, skill-based platforming challenges.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through 10 unique retro game inspired biomes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Precision controls and a unique collection of power-ups</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face an array of different A.I. monsters that learn and evolve as they fight you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use your skills to run, jump, dash, swim, fly, and stomp your way to victory</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50 stages of challenges, danger, and an obscene amount of spikes!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/eacd3cbbd4cd15050f25b035ebece7a6.poster.avif?t=1749610118\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/eacd3cbbd4cd15050f25b035ebece7a6.webm?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/eacd3cbbd4cd15050f25b035ebece7a6.mp4?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And if you've read this far you should also know: this game was entirely made by a single developer. Story, art, music, programming, design, everything in this game was made by a single person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/488bc9492642dc8356afac803752e99d.poster.avif?t=1749610118\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/488bc9492642dc8356afac803752e99d.webm?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304910/extras/488bc9492642dc8356afac803752e99d.mp4?t=1749610118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
